---
title: Mexican Smashed Chickpeas & Garlic Rice with Pickled Onion Salsa
description: Don’t be fooled by the ‘smashed’ in our Mexican smashed chickpea bowl, this dish is tranquil and easy, perfect for any hectic weekday night. Soothing rice soaks up an ensemble of tastes from the pickled onion and spiced chickpeas. So don’t worry, you can sit back and relax into dinner tonight.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
